<meta name="socialpost1" content="A ProPublica and MLK50 analysis shows that just 17 of more than 800 immigration arrests made by Trump’s crime-fighting task force in and around Memphis were for violent crimes. 82% of the immigration arrests followed a traffic stop." />
<meta name="socialpost2" content="Mayor Paul Young has repeatedly said Trump’s task force is meant to help Memphis police target violent crime, not detain immigrants. That’s not what our data analysis shows." />
<meta name="socialpost3" content="Trump’s Memphis task force was supposed to target violent criminals. But in the first 4 months, just over a quarter of 5,200+ arrests made by the force in and around Memphis were for violent crimes, ProPublica and @mlk50memphis found." />
